ForgedTTC — licensing (open-core split, decision D2/D24)

Copyright 2026 RNT56

This repository contains two license zones:

1. THE OPEN CORE — Apache License 2.0
   Scope:  crates/        (the forge-* core: contract, geometry, motion,
                           sim, validate, wasm facade, num, gen)
           schema/        (the emitted JSON Schema — the single source)
           examples/      (first-party contracts and fixtures)
   Full license text: LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt
   Attribution file:  NOTICE

   These are the bits that judge a model everywhere (D17). Anyone may use,
   modify, and redistribute them under Apache-2.0, including building
   their own tools on the contract format and validator.

2. EVERYTHING ELSE — proprietary, all rights reserved
   Scope:  packages/      (studio, gateway)
           workers/       (compute workers)
           prototype/     (the frozen reference implementation)
           catalog/       (component rows; data provenance per row)
           docs/, infra/, scripts/ and all other paths
   Copyright 2026 RNT56. No license is granted. Do not copy, modify, or
   redistribute without written permission.

Component catalog rows under catalog/ additionally carry their own
licenseClass field (D10) governing each asset's export and redistribution;
cited manufacturer specifications remain the property of their publishers.

Contributions: by submitting a contribution to a path in zone 1 you agree
to license it under Apache-2.0; contributions to zone 2 are accepted only
under a grant of rights to RNT56.
